
Need to install jest. for that

npm installl --save-dev jest

for asynchronous fetch calls, need to install 'node-fetch' as node does not have access to window fetch method

for that install

npm install node-fetch

to run js files: type: node <filename>
eg: node script.js
node script2.js

and to run test: type  - npm test (watch has been applied in package.json test command to watch all changes in js files)
npm test - will automatically execute all files that has test.js or spec.js extensions